{
  "stem": "27687.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I was alone, but that's fine, and I worked and so on and was good for about I would say maybe-- so that was-- that was about late summer, about two months-- August, September, October.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '41.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was about October.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in '41 somebody came from a delegation from the occupied part of France to recruit people to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they came down one morning, and we had to get out from the-- from the barracks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they looked us over, and they said you, you, you, you, you, you, come this way and fine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they marched us to a different barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Inside that barrack, they somehow had organized different parts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we had to undress, and there were two-- I think they were doctors-- they were sitting there on a desk.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were checking us over, and so I heard one doctor say to the other, and he said you know-- pointing at me-- he said look at how he looks.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He is quite skinny.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Oh, the other doctor said, oh, don't worry about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We give him something good to eat, and he will be able to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I figured, well, that sounds better.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in Southern France, still in--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In German, ya.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, they were SS doctors, you see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, oh, that-- to myself, I thought, well, that sounds not too bad, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so while I was alone, I couldn't say goodbye to my mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't say goodbye to my father, because they didn't let us go anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They gave us different clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- we couldn't get that clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- we undressed in this room, and we went to the other room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They checked us over, and then we went this way.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
